To produce a new openjpeg release (Win32, Linux or OSX):
[replace '1.5' with the current version number, eg '1.5.1']

1. Generate the CHANGES for the release:

$ ./genchange.sh

copy the branch

$ svn copy https://openjpeg.googlecode.com/svn/branches/openjpeg-2.0 https://openjpeg.googlecode.com/svn/tags/version.2.0
$ svn add CHANGES ../../tags/version.2.0
$ svn commit

2. Generates the source tarball + binary tarball (OSX package on Mac):

$ ./release.sh

If you have a windows box, from a CMD console:

> release.bat

You can use googlecode_upload.py to upload your files directly:

# SOURCES
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 source files of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-All,Type-Source /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0.tar.gz

# LINUX (32 bits)
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Linux 32-bits Binaries of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-Linux,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-Linux-i386.tar.gz

# LINUX (64 bits)
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Linux 64-bits Binaries of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-Linux,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-Linux-x86_64.tar.gz

# Mac OSX 32-bit Universal (for Intel or PPC, Tiger/10.4 or later)
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Mac OSX 32-bit Universal Binaries (for Intel or PPC, Tiger/10.4 or later) of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-OSX,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-Darwin-universal.dmg
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Mac OSX 32-bit Universal Binaries (for Intel or PPC, Tiger/10.4 or later) of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-OSX,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-Darwin-universal.tar.gz

# Mac OSX 64/32-bit Universal (for Intel, Snow Leopard/10.6 or later)
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Mac OSX 64/32-bit Universal DMG Package (for Intel, Snow Leopard/10.6 or later) of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-OSX,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-Darwin64-universal.dmg
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Mac OSX 64/32-bit Universal Binaries (for Intel, Snow Leopard/10.6 or later) of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-OSX,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-Darwin64-universal.tar.gz

# Windows (32bits)
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Windows Installer of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-Windows,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-win32-x86.exe
$ ./googlecode_upload.py -s "Version 2.0 Windows Binaries of OpenJPEG library and codecs" -p openjpeg -l Featured,OpSys-Windows,Type-Executable /tmp/openjpeg_release/openjpeg-build/openjpeg-2.0.0-win32-x86.zip 

